sentences: On the agenda (FCCC/SBSTA/2013/4), SBSTA Chair Muyungi proposed including a new sub-item on clarification of the text in section G, Article 3.7 ter of the Doha Amendment under the item on methodological issues under the Protocol.
Parties agreed, adopting the agenda and agreeing to the organization of work.
The SBSTA also agreed that parties submit their opening statements to the Secretariat for posting online.
